=head1 NAME

git-verify - Verify server configuration settings.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

  git-verify [ gituser@git-server-host-name.com ] [ /path/to/server/repo.git ]

Default is to check the current server where the command is run.

=head1 DESCRIPTION

Command-line utility to verify git server configuration for capabilities that could be used by git-server.

